com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface FileSystemContent

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
DataFile, Directory, UnixDirectory, WindowsDirectory
All Known Implementing Classes:
DataFileImpl, DirectoryImpl, FileSystemContentImpl, UnixDirectoryImpl, WindowsDirectoryImpl
public interface FileSystemContent
extends com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability

A representation of the model object 'File System Content'.

The following features are supported:

  • Fixed Path
  • Group
  • Last Modified
  • Owner
  • Permissions
  • Real File
  • Size
  • URI

See Also:
OsPackage.getFileSystemContent()
